<h2>Welcome to the Fairwood Explorer Portal</h2>

<p>
  This application provides some online services for the Fairwood Explorer community.
</p>

<h3>Afterschool Activities Enrollment Service</h3>
<p>
  This is the enrollment service for afterschool activities offered by the Fairwood
  Explorer program.
</p>
<p>
  Please
  <% unless current_parent %>
    <%= link_to "sign up", new_parent_registration_path %> for an account,
  <% end %>
  register your students
  <% unless current_parent %>,
  <% end %>
  and then enroll into activities.
</p>
<p>
  Contact <%= mail_to(ENV['ASA_EMAIL'], ENV['ASA_ADMIN_NAME']) %>
  of the Afterschool Activities Team for questions about activities.
  Contact the <%= mail_to('fairwood-techsupport@googlegroups.com', 'IT') %> team for
  technical issues with the site.
</p>
<h3>Walkathon Pledge Service</h3>
<p>
  This service enables sponsors to make pledges for Fairwood students, and it allows parents to
  track pledges for their students, including the status of pledge payments.
</p>
<p>
  Click on the button for the service you are interested in at the top of this page.
</p>